===Etymology===
* {{sense|coded warning}} Originally used in [[shearing]] [[shed]]s; later extended to other normally all-male environments, such as some pubs.<ref>[http://andc.anu.edu.au/australian-words/meanings-origins?field_alphabet_value=91 Australian National Dictionary Centre » Australian words » Meanings and origins of Australian words and idioms » D]</ref>

